        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-12de153a-e66e-4278-b0cf-aa9d9ca6a28c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-12de153a-e66e-4278-b0cf-aa9d9ca6a28c">
                Mr. Gallacher
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-12de153a-e66e-4278-b0cf-aa9d9ca6a28c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-05-09/debates/4fecc438-24a7-48c3-8c7e-cc7852ac591b/Jamaica(LabourConditions)#contribution-12de153a-e66e-4278-b0cf-aa9d9ca6a28c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Secretary of State for the Colonies whether in view of the fact that wages of under 2s. a day are being paid by Messrs. Tate and Lyle to their employé's on sugar plantations in Jamaica, he will take steps to institute a minimum wage for that island?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-12de153a-e66e-4278-b0cf-aa9d9ca6a28c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-05-09/debates/4fecc438-24a7-48c3-8c7e-cc7852ac591b/Jamaica(LabourConditions)#contribution-12de153a-e66e-4278-b0cf-aa9d9ca6a28c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-cb0924f0-9b3d-4055-8402-aa934ad6f7df">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-cb0924f0-9b3d-4055-8402-aa934ad6f7df">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-cb0924f0-9b3d-4055-8402-aa934ad6f7df">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-cb0924f0-9b3d-4055-8402-aa934ad6f7df">
                The Vice-Chamberlain of the Household (Mr. Cross)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-cb0924f0-9b3d-4055-8402-aa934ad6f7df" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-05-09/debates/4fecc438-24a7-48c3-8c7e-cc7852ac591b/Jamaica(LabourConditions)#contribution-cb0924f0-9b3d-4055-8402-aa934ad6f7df">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I have been asked to reply. The Governor has recently appointed, with my right hon. Friend's <span id="1233" class="column-number" data-column-number="1233"></span> approval, two Commissioners to examine labour conditions generally and to collect particulars of the wages of the lowest-paid classes of labourers. It would be premature to attempt to fix a minimum wage until the Commissioners have reported and the Governor has made recommendations on the report. My right hon. Friend has no particulars regarding the various rates of wages now being paid, but from such information as is available it appears that the average daily wage of field labourers on the plantations in question is in excess of the figure quoted by the hon. Member.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-cb0924f0-9b3d-4055-8402-aa934ad6f7df" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-05-09/debates/4fecc438-24a7-48c3-8c7e-cc7852ac591b/Jamaica(LabourConditions)#contribution-cb0924f0-9b3d-4055-8402-aa934ad6f7df">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-fc745cc2-9c4d-4814-bf74-d103c6ac3aff">
